The article announces several nominations and appointments made on August 1, 2018. Kelvin Droegemeier is nominated to be the Director of the Office of Science and Technology Policy, replacing John P. Holdren. Carol Z. Perez is appointed as the Director General of the Foreign Service, replacing Arnold A. Chacon, who resigned. Joel Szabat is appointed as an Assistant Secretary of Transportation, replacing Susan L. Kurland, who resigned.